{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/2017/01/25/jekyll-on-ubuntu/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"<bbon />","siteUrl":"https://bbon.me"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"7ed5f586-0c24-5489-a888-6aa62c695ec5","excerpt":"RVM Ruby Version Manager 설치 패키지를 갱신합니다. RVM을 설치하기 위해 curl을 설치합니다. RVM을 설치합니다. 설치후 프로파일 추가사항 적용을 위해 아래 명령을 실행합니다. 루비 설치 RVM…","html":"<h2><a href=\"https://rvm.io/\">RVM <small>Ruby Version Manager</small></a> 설치</h2>\n<p>패키지를 갱신합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> update</code></pre></div>\n<p>RVM을 설치하기 위해 curl을 설치합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token function\">curl</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://rvm.io/\">RVM</a>을 설치합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ gpg --keyserver hkp://keys.gnupg.net --recv-keys 409B6B1796C275462A1703113804BB82D39DC0E3</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>curl -sSL https://get.rvm.io <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">bash</span> -s stable</code></pre></div>\n<p>설치후 프로파일 추가사항 적용을 위해 아래 명령을 실행합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> ~/.rvm/scripts/rvm</code></pre></div>\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.ruby-lang.org/ko/\">루비</a> 설치</h2>\n<p>RVM을 사용하여 <a href=\"https://www.ruby-lang.org/ko/\">루비</a>를 설치합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ rvm <span class=\"token function\">install</span> ruby-2.4.0</code></pre></div>\n<p>설치된 루비 버전 확인합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ ruby -v</code></pre></div>\n<h2><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/ko/\">Nodejs</a> 설치</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">curl</span> -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_4.x <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> -E <span class=\"token function\">bash</span> -</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -y nodejs</code></pre></div>\n<h2><a href=\"https://jekyllrb.com/\">Jekyll</a> 설치</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ gem <span class=\"token function\">install</span> jekyll</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Jekyll on Ubuntu","date":"January 25, 2017","description":"Jekyll on Ubuntu","categories":["computing"],"tags":["jekyll","ruby","nodejs"],"github":null,"featuredImage":null,"draft":null,"comments":false}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2016/12/15/web-storage-api/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Javascript Web Storage API","draft":null,"comments":false,"featuredImage":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2017/03/29/ios-10-3/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"iOS 10.3","draft":null,"comments":false,"featuredImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"7ed5f586-0c24-5489-a888-6aa62c695ec5","previousPostId":"ffb2ea9e-cb49-567f-ab3d-ddc36db9a46b","nextPostId":"1790dede-47fa-5b54-a1e0-69d2b112d6a4"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2644450635","3199328057"]}